'''亞伯達倫'''（Aberdaron）是[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]的一個城鎮，位於[[麗茵半島|麗茵半島]]的西端，[[普爾黑利|普爾黑利]]以西{{convert|14.8|mi|km}}，[[卡那芬|卡那芬]]西南{{convert|33.5|mi|km}}，人口有965人<ref name="population">{{cite web|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790560|title=Census 2001: Parish Headcounts: Gwynedd|publisher=Office for National Statistics|accessdate=16 August 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922091920/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790560|archivedate=2010年9月22日}}</ref>。亞伯達倫有威爾斯的天涯海角之稱。
